rt-magnet is a PHP-based addon to handle magnetlinks for the GNU/Linux 
torrent client rTorrent (http://libtorrent.rakshasa.no/). You get to 
choose which directory every magnetlink torrent is to be saved, all 
according to your alread defined watch directories. Please see the HOWTO
document for installation instructions.

REQUIREMENTS
It is necessary to have watch directories configured and used by 
rTorrent in order to make use of rt-magnet. You will also need a 
webserver running, like Apache or similar, to reach the GUI with your 
web browser.
